com.tractrac.model.lib.impl.spatial

Class Coordinate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tractrac.model.lib.impl.spatial.Coordinate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICoordinate

    public class Coordinate
extends java.lang.Object
implements ICoordinate
    A lightweight class used to store raw coordinates Coordinates are two-dimensional points, with an additional z-ordinate and m-ordinate. If z and m ordinate values are undefined, a value of NaN is returned.
    Author:
    Jesper Grooss
